7394,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:23:45.000Z","msg":"我係出面叫人睇路個PO 好撚多P牌同鬼AC負皮<br />\n<br />\n824 825已經暴露左對家想亂拉製造白色恐怖 <br />\n尋晚更加係 有五個FULL GEAR 一出就幾十部狗車圍<br />\n<br />\n想同慶賀 麻煩集中101先請小鳳姐出場<br />\n<br />\n一堆人負皮我 但係全部係鳩屌 同班狗開鬼AC帶風向一撚樣<br />\n淨係識屌 唔撚比有建設性意見"},{"pid":"780d02bcf86670934c00ea6b8ecaa534cd53552f","tid":1517394,"uid":46014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:56:39.000Z","msg":"請各位謹慎<br />\n敵人用嘅手法越嗱咋、越肉酸，代表佢哋好急，亦可能意味我哋就嚟逼到佢哋上絕路<br />\n但逼喺牆角嘅老鼠，隨時會反咬一口<br />\n我哋一定要小心行每一步，唔好辜負呢兩個幾月嚟各位犧牲咗嘅或者受到摧殘嘅手足"},{"pid":"4c07280af9845e193a2e93166700264d00839ad8","tid":1517394,"uid":46014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:35:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1066871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1066871&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8vo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=f3424c93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1066871&h=a7a6259b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1066871</a><br />\n今朝仲有個區議員被拘捕"},{"pid":"27d2d059a0897f709ea046f03ef4d18fb7acc66a","tid":1517394,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0210d8c9ccd16adf5450c2b381170022265917c0","tid":1517394,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:23:45.000Z","msg":"我係出面叫人睇路個PO 好撚多P牌同鬼AC負皮<br />\n<br />\n824 825已經暴露左對家想亂拉製造白色恐怖 <br />\n尋晚更加係 有五個FULL GEAR 一出就幾十部狗車圍<br />\n<br />\n想同慶賀 麻煩集中101先請小鳳姐出場<br />\n<br />\n一堆人負皮我 但係全部係鳩屌 同班狗開鬼AC帶風向一撚樣<br />\n淨係識屌 唔撚比有建設性意見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:37:37.000Z","msg":"9.30預祝強國啦，等睇10.1取消煙花。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa287bdfb1ca4a65df05eea1121a9bc0967e5536","tid":1517394,"uid":30115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:40:56.000Z","msg":"遊擊戰術please"},{"pid":"7d3709e1bdfb0506dfa6d857ef428c11dce20720","tid":1517394,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:43:38.000Z","msg":"前線忍忍 <br />\n要頂到10月"},{"pid":"80fcfcc7090f94bed921ceb15c1f12fdd3317b69","tid":1517394,"uid":265179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:47:03.000Z","msg":"王丹网站 Wang Dan's Page<br />\n4 hrs &middot; <br />\n岑子杰被襲擊，黃之鋒被捕，陳浩天被拒絕離境。大逮捕就要開始了。中共顯然是要抓捕大部分有號召力的抗爭組織者。<br />\n<br />\n鎮壓的時刻就要到了。港人退無可退。必須保護黃之鋒這些人，否則，下一個被捕的人就是你。<br />\n<br />\n831大遊行，當局會評估港人面對進一步鎮壓的抗壓度。那將是關鍵時刻。希望港人都站出來。<br />\n<br />\n也再次呼籲台灣的民間團體或者政黨，能夠發動大遊行，聲援和救救香港！"},{"pid":"6c9dde16346a890b6596648883a1fd922180e72f","tid":1517394,"uid":46014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:53:43.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰都俾人拉埋"},{"pid":"2a5bf18d9c2c538a8bd82c83c7caa86722d528fe","tid":1517394,"uid":46014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T20:13:01.000Z","msg":"大家千萬要小心<br />\n對面應該想盡快完結事件"},{"pid":"c95334456102ee08c8ecfe69f9cc44884b0ae4b1","tid":1517394,"uid":46014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T20:48:43.000Z","msg":"各位手足唔好衝動行事<br />\n831絕對唔係最後一戰<br />\n記住留返條命，就算貼街招都係對對方嘅威脅"},{"pid":"f6814d8d1cce13bb3efe831de77ae27f6486a809","tid":1517394,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T20:51:40.000Z","msg":"嚇你唔敢出就真"},{"pid":"4e180ab837da88605bb5c985c4c23457a26510b5","tid":1517394,"uid":60488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T20:52:59.000Z","msg":"越多人就越安全 人多驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2fcceb080ac6391a017791605e61395f3c0b59","tid":1517394,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T20:53:51.000Z","msg":"停鐵就要be water 準備游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093b7e4fd85350dfa2fc0596ac92d549206839f3","tid":1517394,"uid":173058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T21:57:4